title: Clean Your Room
author: Krystanburge
pages:
#- I fucking hate my parents. All they ever do is boss me the fuck around. Today I'm fed the fuck up with their shit, I'm going to end this fucking misery. I'm tired of all of their saintly christ bullshit, and how they treat Sarah so much better than me.
#- "Connor, why can't you be like Sarah?" "Connor, clean your room." "Connor, we love you, we're just scared for you.."
Damn fucking straight  I'll give you a reason to be scared for me you cunts. I'm going to fucking kill you all in your sleep. I'll
#- lacerate your veins and piss in them and shove a fucking rosary in your god damned intestines. I'll facefuck your lifeless bloody body. I swear to god, if the first grade sucks this bad life isn't worth living anyways. I'm done writing
#- and contemplating about this shit.
#- 